function Start()
	local sChest = ACTOR_CHEST_REWARD

	if Hydra.QuestGetBonusPhaseResult() then
		sChest = ACTOR_CHEST_REWARD_HEROIC
	end
	
	Events.SpawnRewardChest(CHEST_LOCATION, sChest)
end

function Start(idActorSpawned, idActorSpawner)
	
	if B_SHRINE_ALIVE then
		Hydra.ActorMergeAIState(idActorSpawned, STATE_CHANNELER, idActorSpawned, 0)
	end
	
end

function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)
	Hydra.ActorSetPowerEffectSize(ID_VFX_LOC, 6)
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(ID_VFX_LOC, EG_LOSS)
end

function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)
	local ptWalkTo = Hydra.ActorGetPosition(ID_SHRINE_MONSTER)
	ptWalkTo = Hydra.PositionSearchForNearbyNavmeshPosition(ptWalkTo, 12, 16, true, false)
	
	Hydra.QActorPlaySimpleConversation(CONVO_THANK, ID_SHRINE_MONSTER)
	Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(ID_SHRINE_MONSTER)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToPositionDynamicSpeed(ID_SHRINE_MONSTER, ptWalkTo, "NPC_Walk")
	Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(ID_SHRINE_MONSTER, 2)
	
	
end

function Start()
	--make it look like a ritual has been completed
	Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdate(DEMONS)
end

function Start(flTimeRemaining)
	-- Explode Shrine
	Hydra.ActorSetPowerEffectSize(ID_VFX_LOC, 16)
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(ID_VFX_LOC, EG_WIN_EXPLODE)
end

function Start(flGameTime)
	
	if Hydra.BuffIsOnActor(POWER_CHANNEL, "CHANNELING_BUFF", ID_SHRINE_MONSTER) then
		Hydra.EventSend("RITUAL_PROGRESSED", idSelf)
	end

end

function Start(idActor, flPrevHP, flHp)
	Hydra.ActorSetInvulnerable(ID_SHRINE_MONSTER, true)
	Hydra.ActorSetPowerEffectSize(ID_SHRINE_MONSTER, 12)
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(ID_SHRINE_MONSTER, EG_CHARGE, true)
	Hydra.QActorPlaySimpleConversation(CONVO_DEATH, ID_SHRINE_MONSTER)
	Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(ID_SHRINE_MONSTER, CONVO_DEATH)
	Hydra.QActorKill(ID_SHRINE_MONSTER)
end

for i, monsterID in pairs(Hydra.ActorsInPrefabScopedGroup(PSAG_CHANNELERS)) do
	Hydra.ActorRemoveMergedAIState(monsterID, STATE_CHANNELER)
end

B_SHRINE_ALIVE = false

for i, spawnerID in pairs(T_SPAWNERS_ALL) do
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(spawnerID) then
		Hydra.ActorDelete(spawnerID)
	end
end

unk_993f312.value:
-- Event Specific Data			
B_SHRINE_ALIVE = true

PSAG_CHANNELERS = "LE_Shrine_Channelers"

for i, actorID in pairs(Hydra.ActorsInPrefabScopedGroup(PSAG_CHANNELERS)) do --incase background doesn't catch initial channelers
	Hydra.ActorMergeAIState(actorID, STATE_CHANNELER, actorID, 0)
end

Events.ActorSetPhased(ID_SHRINE_MONSTER, true)
